Text: I want to be simple and straight forward I want this trip to meet my long distance
  girlfriend and this travel opportunity fits everything right, until April 30 I will
  have 17 plus my parents can sign an approval so I can go, please take into consideration
  This means a lot to me, I would also love to visit the place, thank you very much.
